# Copy to `.env` and fill in. `.env` is gitignored; this file is the tracked reference.

## Deploy (optional) — used by `npm run build`'s postbuild hook to FTP-upload.
## NOTE: `npm run build` PUBLISHES. Use `npm run testbuild` to build without uploading.
# DEPLOY_COMMAND=
# FULL_DEPLOY_COMMAND=

## The "AI" button (optional) — origin of the natural-language → session Worker
## (mcp/worker). Leave unset and the button never appears; AnCiR works exactly as before.
##
## ⚠️ VITE_* vars are INLINED INTO THE BROWSER BUNDLE, so this must never hold a secret.
## It doesn't need to: the model's API key lives as a Worker-side secret
## (`npx wrangler secret put OPENAI_API_KEY`), and this app never sees one. A user may
## supply their own key in the modal's Advanced tab; it's passed through for that one
## request and never stored.
# VITE_ANCIR_NL_URL=https://ancir-nl.david-cumin.workers.dev
